headline: Healthpeak Properties Publishes Its 14th Annual Corporate Impact Report
summary: DENVER, September 04, 2025--Healthpeak Properties, Inc. ("Healthpeak") (NYSE: DOC) announced today the release of its 14th annual 2024 Corporate Impact Report (the "Report"). The Report highlights Healthpeak’s continued focus on building a resilient portfolio, advancing sustainability goals, fostering a workplace culture guided by its WE CARE core values, and promoting sound corporate governance and transparency.
